 * version 0.1
  - added a game menu
  - added a spectrum mode (no damage) in order to easily test new levels
	- added a new level (level 5) with new decors (tunnels)
	- added a "configure / make / make install" system using the autotools

 * version 0.02
  - rewrite the whole game in C++
	- added options
	- added T3FWidgets library
	- added sounds

 * version 0.01
   First release of the game. AlThreat is a shoot'em up in C/SDL programmed to
	 be evolutive. You can easily add/modify levels, bonus ...
